{"tid":730994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"默克爾：支持降低進口美國車關稅","createTime":"2018-07-06T00:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T02:03:38.000Z","uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d5b01916a4121bf1a90b24345a3b83dde34b43cf","tid":730994,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:48:42.000Z","msg":"默克爾：支持降低進口美國車關稅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2108976/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8A%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2108976%2F%25E9%25BB%2598%25E5%2585%258B%25E7%2588%25BE%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E9%2599%258D%25E4%25BD%258E%25E9%2580%25B2%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25BB%258A%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585&d=AL1i7qRJf9X35M36L0oE2sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=e7b54aa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2108976/%E9%BB%98%E5%85%8B%E7%88%BE%EF%BC%9A%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E9%99%8D%E4%BD%8E%E9%80%B2%E5%8F%A3%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%BB%8A%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85</a><br />\n<br />\n德國總理默克爾（Angela Merkel）表示，願意支持歐盟降低對進口美國車徵收的關稅，以回應美方有意放棄調高對歐洲車徵稅的讓步。<br />\n<br />\n路透社早前引述消息指，美國駐德國大使格雷內爾（Richard Grenell）多次與德國福士（Volkswagen）、寶馬（BMW）、戴姆勒（Daimler）等車廠高層會晤，並透露美國總統特朗普有意放棄調高對歐洲進口車的關稅，但前提是歐盟取消對美國進口車徵稅。<br />\n<br />\n相關車廠高層均拒絕回應報道。<br />\n<br />\n默克爾則表示，願意支持降低關稅的談判，但歐盟不能只對美國減關稅。她重申，任何降低美國進口車關稅的舉措，同樣需要降低來自其他國家的進口車，以便符合世界貿易組織（WTO）規定。"},{"pid":"fc6d29fba787d3c558350da6dc8b86af5aea3062","tid":730994,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"默克爾則表示，願意支持降低關稅的談判，但歐盟不能只對美國減關稅。她重申，任何降低美國進口車關稅的舉措，同樣需要降低來自其他國家的進口車，以便符合世界貿易組織（WTO）規定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠又禍國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n侵侵又靠把口贏一場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59ae15f0878fb95006ccfb76c07efc83e43ce57","tid":730994,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc6d29fba787d3c558350da6dc8b86af5aea3062","tid":730994,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T00:59:54.000Z","msg":"默克爾則表示，願意支持降低關稅的談判，但歐盟不能只對美國減關稅。她重申，任何降低美國進口車關稅的舉措，同樣需要降低來自其他國家的進口車，以便符合世界貿易組織（WTO）規定。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n左膠又禍國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n侵侵又靠把口贏一場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"佢本身要成個歐盟同意先可以減稅<br />\n仲話要對全球一齊減<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b65ef360d94c56598caff6fcb226a3712c7dbb3","tid":730994,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"支那仲話想拉攏歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人地歐美之間有計傾傢<br />\n點同你支那嗰套贏國思維<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b065566ab1a28e2f2492ba5247700edd8b84c84","tid":730994,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T02:00:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4567b0b2be944cc61266d3e4e7195e4551ba926","tid":730994,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b65ef360d94c56598caff6fcb226a3712c7dbb3","tid":730994,"uid":98289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T01:44:18.000Z","msg":"支那仲話想拉攏歐盟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hk